### 平台治理基线验证（幂等 / CSRF / 权限 / 多租户）

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@tenantA = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@tenantB = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000999
@username = admin
@password = P@ssw0rd!
@idemKey = 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111

### 登录（租户 A）
# @name loginA
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantA}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@tokenA = {{loginA.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 获取 CSRF
# @name antiforgeryA
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/secure/antiforgery
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantA}}

###
@csrfA = {{antiforgeryA.response.body.$.data.token}}

### 幂等验证：第一次创建表格视图（应成功）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/table-views
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantA}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{csrfA}}
Idempotency-Key: {{idemKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tableKey": "system.users",
  "name": "治理基线幂等视图",
  "config": {
    "columns": [{ "key": "username", "visible": true, "order": 0 }],
    "density": "default",
    "pagination": { "pageSize": 10 }
  }
}

### 幂等验证：相同 key + 相同 payload（应返回相同结果）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/table-views
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantA}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{csrfA}}
Idempotency-Key: {{idemKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tableKey": "system.users",
  "name": "治理基线幂等视图",
  "config": {
    "columns": [{ "key": "username", "visible": true, "order": 0 }],
    "density": "default",
    "pagination": { "pageSize": 10 }
  }
}

### 幂等冲突：相同 key + 不同 payload（应返回 409 IDEMPOTENCY_CONFLICT）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/table-views
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantA}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{csrfA}}
Idempotency-Key: {{idemKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tableKey": "system.users",
  "name": "治理基线幂等视图-冲突版本",
  "config": {
    "columns": [{ "key": "displayName", "visible": true, "order": 0 }],
    "density": "compact",
    "pagination": { "pageSize": 20 }
  }
}

### CSRF 缺失（应返回 400/403）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/table-views
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantA}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$randomUUID}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tableKey": "system.users",
  "name": "csrf-missing",
  "config": {
    "columns": [{ "key": "username", "visible": true, "order": 0 }]
  }
}

### 多租户隔离：租户 A token + 租户 B header（应拒绝）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantB}}

### 权限控制：不带 token 访问受保护资源（应 401）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantA}}

### 迁移治理指标总览（P1）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/migration-governance/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantA}}

